=============
A simple ftpd
=============

* Requirement 
Java 5 or higher.


* Quick start
$ ant 
$ java -jar rath-ftpd.jar 

Done! 


* Adding a new user 
1) Open ftpd.properties
2) If username you want to add is 'git' and desired password is 'hub', 
   add 2 lines like below

   ftp.home.git=/home/git
   ftp.user.git=hub

3) Save the file and exit. 
4) Restart the server. 

